This template can be used to indicate the author of a comment when said author has forgotten to sign with three or four tildes (<code><nowiki>~~~</nowiki></code> or <code><nowiki>~~~~</nowiki></code>).

For example, using
<pre>{{unsigned|timestamp|username}}</pre>
produces: {{unsigned|timestamp|username}}. This form is quite practical as the template parameters can be copied and pasted directly from the page history.

The following short form is also possible:
<pre>{{unsigned|username}}</pre>
produces just {{unsigned|username}}.

